# Development Workflow

## Getting Started
1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

2. Start the development server:
   ```bash
   npm run tauri dev
   ```

## Project Structure
- Frontend code is in the [src/](mdc:src) directory
- Backend code is in the [src-tauri/](mdc:src-tauri) directory
- Custom React hooks are in the [hooks/](mdc:hooks) directory

## Key Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) contains all npm scripts and dependencies
- [src-tauri/Cargo.toml](mdc:src-tauri/Cargo.toml) contains Rust dependencies
- [src-tauri/tauri.conf.json](mdc:src-tauri/tauri.conf.json) configures the Tauri application

## Building
- Development build: `npm run tauri dev`
- Production build: `npm run tauri build`

## Testing
- Run tests: `npm test`
- Run type checking: `npm run type-check`
